{"id":232836257,"title":"總統選舉前該做什麼選擇權策略？","content":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxA2fbUoX_0\n(重點可以從8分8秒開始看起)\n \n期貨只能賭一邊，50%的機率\n但如果用選擇權的話，如果認為會出現大漲大跌\n都可以用這樣的策略，買進買權也買進賣權\n\n只怕是小漲小跌或完全沒動\n那就會承受買賣權兩邊一起虧損\n另外，如果有什麼重要經濟數據公布\n也是可以運用這樣的策略\n並不是限定只有選舉才能用唷 (*ﾟ∀ﾟ*) \n\n但近幾年看起來只有在盤中才能看到大漲或大跌\n等到收盤就又往中間靠攏\n如果這樣的策略要繼續持有到結算的話\n可能要承擔的theta風險就會比較重\n\n最後，不管你要做什麼策略\n都記得要出來投票嘿 (๑•̀ㅂ•́)و✧","excerpt":"（重點可以從8分8秒開始看起），期貨只能賭一邊，50%的機率，但如果用選擇權的話，如果認為會出現大漲大跌，都可以用這樣的策略，買進買權也買進賣權，只怕是小漲小跌或完全沒動，那就會承受買賣權兩邊一起虧損","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"3bceb81c-574e-4a96-8050-4df56096d0df","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-06T08:48:48.521Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-06T08:49:34.918Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":9,"tags":[],"topics":["選擇權","理財","股票","期貨","投資"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"理財","forumAlias":"money","school":"選擇權玩家凱文","department":"optionplayer","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":9}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"93e8dc5a-f96f-449f-8349-dd360dc0f2b3","url":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/kxA2fbUoX_0/hqdefault.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/kxA2fbUoX_0/hqdefault.jpg","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/kxA2fbUoX_0/hqdefault.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-06T08:48:48.521Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-06T08:49:34.918Z"},{"id":"93e8dc5a-f96f-449f-8349-dd360dc0f2b3","url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxA2fbUoX_0","normalizedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxA2fbUoX_0","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/kxA2fbUoX_0/hqdefault.jpg","type":"video/youtube","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-06T08:48:48.521Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-06T08:49:34.918Z"}],"postAv